{
  "stem": "1860.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 427.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were-- we started living in Plaszow concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- the Krakow ghetto was on the-- the point of being liquidated.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all the inhabitants, all the Jews were going to-- to Plaszow camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I really don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't-- I-- I couldn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We walked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We walked from Krakow ghetto to-- to-- to Plaszow with whatever we could carry in our two hands.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A few-- probably, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As far as I can remember, yeah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we arrived in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, of course, this was a shock to see all the sleeping accommodations, the bunk beds.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were three tiers of bunk beds.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If I remember correctly, my mother and I were in the middle bunk bed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my-- my grandmother and my aunt and my cousin had the lower-- lower bunks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were wooden boards with some-- well, we managed to carry with us some pillows and blankets.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So this is what-- what we used to cover ourselves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not when we-- not when we arrived in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From Plaszow, we were going out to work to Optima and coming back for the-- for the night to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember every time we would come back, the first question was, what's the score?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How many were hung, and how many were shot?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because there was always killing going on in Plaszow with this infamous Amon Goth was the commandant of the camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were many selections.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember once we-- we were witnessing hanging of a friend of ours, a young boy who was at that time 17.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Or-- supposedly, he was humming a tune, a Russian tune.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was a good enough reason to-- to hang him for it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] After a while, we stopped working at Optima.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
